<L>__{exterior sheriff's office day}
<A>__{med. full shot angled to include blacksmith shop across the street. far down the street comes graham's buckboard followed by the small crowd. the sheriff's office is a one story wooden structure. next to it is the general store. in front of the blacksmith shop stands a wagon with one wheel off. in the corral alongside are eleven blooded mares. clay phillips, his brother steve and the blacksmith are inside the shop. clay's saddle horse is tethered to the hitching rail beside two harnessed work horses.}
